title: Aeeria Online (0.0.1.6) Full Client
description:
http://aeeria.com/

Latest full client released to play the game Aeeria Online.

Minimum system requirements (Almost any Windows PC / Laptop): 

  - Pentium 233 Mhz, 32 MB RAM 
  - 1 MB RAM video card 
  - 80 Mb Harddisk 
  - Windows 98,ME,2000, XP, Vista, 7, 8 
  - Direct x 7.0 or above 
  - Internet connection

Aeeria Online is a free fantasy-adventure based roleplaying game.
Shape your destiny as a Crusader, Magus or Rogue in the mythical realm of Aeeria.
Play in real-time with your friends and take on challenging raids, battles and tournaments, embark on heroic quests and adventures, test your metal against other players or train followers and pets!

Start Guide
